Ni tu baar baar baar mainu yaad aandi hai

Tu je nedeh rabb vi nedeh

Ni tu baar baar baar mainu yaad aandi hai

Ishq da mulazim main taanh darr tere aayi jaavan

Suraan te taanh rabb vassey tere sur gaayi jaavan
Ik teri khair mangaan tera ban jaavan

Tenu labhde nain ye mere 
Sang tere hi chain ye mere
Bin tere behaal main meri jaan jaandi hai

Haan Tu je nedeh rabb vi nedeh

snippet.title: Rippan Swaamy Official Teaser | Vijay Raghavendra | Kishor Mudubidire | Ashwini Chandrashekar | PRK
snippet.description:
Panchaanana Films productions in association with PRK Audio
presents
Rippan Swaamy - A rural thriller set in the fictional Malnad village of Snana Kopa. The story unfolds after the mysterious suicide of Rippan Swaamy, leading to a trail of secrets, drama, and suspense. As the mystery deepens, the truth behind his name and death slowly unravels.

The film is set to release in theatres on August 29.
Listen to the audio exclusively on PRK Audio. üéµ

snippet.title: Saiyaara (1980) Ft. Kishore Kumar full song (Old version) Old is Gold with a New Voice!
snippet.description:
Saiyaara (1980) Ft. Kishore Kumar full song (Old version) Old is Gold with a New Voice!

The full version is finally here! We converted the vocals sung amazingly by RJ Kisna into kishore da's voice using AI, and I produced the retro background music, let me know if ya'll want a breakdown of how I do these retro versions! 




üåç Follow me here for more fun and behind the scenes:
Instagram - 
@anshuman.sharma1 |   / anshuman.sharma1  
Twitter - @anshumonsharma |   / anshumonsharma  
Facebook - @anshuman.sharma111 |   / anshuman.sharma1  

Saiyaara (1980) ‚Äì Kishore Kumar's Saiyaara Full Song 
Step back in time and relive the golden era of Bollywood with Kishore Kumar's rare gem "Saiyaara" (1980). This soulful melody captures the essence of vintage romance, timeless lyrics, and the golden voice of Kishore Da that still resonates in every heart.

Whether you're a lifelong Kishore fan or discovering his magic for the first time, this song is a journey into the past that you don't want to mi

Credit goes to _Rakesh Sutradhar üôè

[Verse 1]
Tu paas hai mere paas hai aise
Mera koi ehsaas hai jaise

Tu paas hai mere paas hai aise
Mera koi ehsaas hai jaise

Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Baaton mein teri main raatein bitaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

[Chorus]
Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

[Verse 2]
Beetey lamhon se duniya basa loon
Main toh tere aansuon ka bana hoon

Meri hansi mein teri sadaayein
Teri kahaani khud ko sunaaun

Yaadon ke taare, yaadon ke taare tootenge kaise
Mere hain jo woh roothenge kaise

Beetey dinon ki kholi kitaabein
Guzre palon ko kaise bhula dein

Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Baaton mein teri main raatein bitaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

[Chorus Repeat]
Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

[Bridge]
Jis roz hum tum phir se milenge
Yeh saari baatein tujhse kahenge

Duniya mein chaahe ban jaayein jo bhi
Tere bina tab kuch na rahenge

[Outro]
Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Main mar hi jaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon



üëá Let us know your favorite Kishore Kumar song in the comments! üëá
üí¨ What memories does this song bring back for you?

snippet.title: COOLIE Trailer Reaction! | Rajinikanth | Nagarjuna Akkineni | Aamir Khan
snippet.description:
Jaby & Achara react to the explosive trailer for Coolie, marking the fiery return of Rajinikanth in a mass-loaded, emotional action drama.

Directed by Lokesh Kanagaraj (Leo, Vikram), Coolie brings back Rajinikanth (Jailer, Kaala) in a powerful new avatar‚Äîmixing grit, style, and legacy. With Anirudh Ravichander‚Äôs pulse-pounding score and stunning visuals, the film promises high-octane action and deep-rooted emotion.

Jaby & Achara break down the intensity, vintage Rajini swag, and Lokesh‚Äôs signature world-building. Coolie looks like a full-blown cinematic celebration of one of India‚Äôs biggest icons.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.
